'''R4-D1''' was one of the [[Astromech droid/Legends|astromech droids]] [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Darrus Jeht/Legends|Darrus Jeht]] used on his [[Delta-6 Sprite-class starfighter]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], the other being [[R4-D2]]. Like other droid pairs assigned to Delta-6 prototypes, the two droids had a habit of arguing with each other. The two droids could also overwhelm the fighter's systems with input if they both tried to communicate at once, making the vessel unstable.

For these reasons, the [[Delta-7 Aethersprite-class light interceptor|Delta-7 starfighters]] which replaced the Delta-6 used only one astromech. Despite this, Jeht kept flying his prototype using both droids.

